      "comment": "ROCKET ROXY (1) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Bottom Up - Maiden at Warrnambool. Better than latest and can atone here. SUNSET DREAM (2) recorded a 7 length second in a Grade 6 last time 30.62 at this track and trip and also jumping from the same draw. Should be in this for a long way. ASTON TOLHURST (3) missed the frame and safely held latest finishing 6th at this track following on from a win (19.94) at Capalaba the start prior. The form out of his last race has been franked. Better than last start and can bounce back. MR. WONDERFUL (8) will give backers a sight.",
